Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.61,0:01:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 她們倆會交往
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.61,0:01:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風早同學要有特別的人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.71,0:01:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還讓我幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 爽子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.87,0:01:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.72,0:01:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.79,0:02:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我還是辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.64,0:02:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:19:57.42,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,banner;28;0;60,翻譯:キョン 瑤瑤　校譯:キョン　時間:キョン　後期:風一樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.69,0:02:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 是我配不上風早嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.81,0:02:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望爽子能支持我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有爽子能讓我說出心裡話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.98,0:02:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人更適合他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡桃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 胡桃子你和他很配
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:03:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子 那...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.73,0:03:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我沒辦法從心裡支持你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說風早同學好像很特別
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.01,0:03:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 不能幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.21,0:03:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得她對我說心裡話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有別我能幫忙的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡桃她一定和我一樣 風早同學對她來說也是特別的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.61,0:03:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不能幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我很理解胡桃的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 如果是聽你講心事的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.93,0:03:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你不退讓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才 你應該感覺到你和我的差距然後自動退出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:03:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽起來聲音像是從胡桃那邊傳出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是背後有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說你理解什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子你想和風早交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會 我怎麼敢 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那特別的又是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.02,0:04:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他護著你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他對你很親切
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.02,0:04:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那完全是出於好心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要對你好一點 就算不是風早也沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡桃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.22,0:04:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太狡猾了 爽子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只因為人比較陰暗 大家都不理睬你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.23,0:04:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不用做 風早就會幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我這樣可愛又受歡迎的人只能自己努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡桃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受歡迎還真是一件辛苦的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我有因為性格陰暗得到好處了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 就因為你有點可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.04,0:05:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會 我只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 因為自己可愛點就囂張起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 輸贏已分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.28,0:05:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和胡桃說的一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太狡猾了 爽子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不用做 風早就會幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不過是在對風早同學的親切撒嬌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.93,0:06:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要對你好一點 就算不是風早也沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是風早同學 而是別人對我這麼親切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心情還會一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.58,0:06:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 小的們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.56,0:06:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是期待已久的運動會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全班給我拚命去贏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束 散會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 我穿上這紅T恤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.59,0:06:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯眼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去好顯眼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千好強
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.47,0:06:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻勁兒也很顯眼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 我會害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同學 又紅又帥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千看上去真幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生的足球比賽在我們前面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:07:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去加油哦 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.99,0:07:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的好聽 到時候你們別喝倒彩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.60,0:07:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會好好加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我們身上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 完成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好適合你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.89,0:07:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很合適
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.33,0:07:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:07:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,座敷童子效應啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.19,0:08:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也試一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.99,0:08:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要 我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好運來 好運
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.75,0:08:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我預感能贏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.36,0:08:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能贏能贏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.23,0:08:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家把你當福星了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.88,0:08:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞子你翻身了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像成為班級的一員了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風早效應嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對風早同學的這種心情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為他總是幫助我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.27,0:08:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是什麼特別的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷停補時3比2啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們班女生能保持住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能吧 赤鬼她很熱血呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.45,0:09:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她想要多顯眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.17,0:09:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過貞子好像不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.26,0:09:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 她在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 龍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.14,0:09:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 又看不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬間移動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過貞子現在融入班級了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.22,0:09:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從和吉田還有矢野成為朋友以後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.07,0:09:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像變得有些開朗了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 到沒有人的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.32,0:09:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.26,0:09:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預 備
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:09:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踢到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.77,0:10:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踢 踢到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風早
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.17,0:10:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.46,0:10:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝負已分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.06,0:10:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4-2
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽結束
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了 幹得好 貞子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高興 第一次像這樣和大家一起高興
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自主訓練的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自主訓練 萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風早 去開比賽之前的作戰會議
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥 你們一會兒有比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.91,0:11:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 軟式棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我好好地加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好的加油 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.01,0:11:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩膀好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.37,0:12:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣勢 氣勢 要靠氣勢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.35,0:12:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我們會贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹的好 貞子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.93,0:12:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野我呢 我可是功不可沒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常顯眼 紅的要命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.27,0:12:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面是我們排球的練習了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.15,0:12:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起來了 比賽之前的大特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.65,0:12:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到比賽開始還有1個多小時
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞子你怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去撿鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踢到哪裡去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.12,0:12:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心使過勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.14,0:12:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你去撿鞋 然後去看我們的練習...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.00,0:12:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 貞子要去給棒球加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們看不了男生的棒球了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要加上我們的份一起加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:12:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:13:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 一會兒見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會去給排球比賽加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.00,0:13:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.07,0:13:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要輸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.51,0:13:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指加油大戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要輸什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足球不是贏了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 別問了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡桃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.43,0:13:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡桃你幫我撿回來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡桃幫貞子撿鞋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.76,0:13:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你 爽子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.39,0:14:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好女孩 果然是好女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 昨天我好像有些得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.05,0:14:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.01,0:14:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡桃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再叫我胡桃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.58,0:14:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.52,0:14:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要認真地把爽子記入「叫我小梅的人」的名單裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.33,0:14:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現在小胡桃的日記
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那是什麼反應啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 小梅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:14:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要叫我小梅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「小梅」是我唯一自卑的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.21,0:15:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.44,0:15:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.58,0:15:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶起的這麼土的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.63,0:15:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一點也不配
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土氣嗎　很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.34,0:15:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.03,0:15:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是貞子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.76,0:15:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是爽子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很好聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.38,0:15:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 她從一開始就叫我爽子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 可以的話一起去操場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要和你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.69,0:15:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有比賽哦 而且風早同學會出場
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:16:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那肯定要去看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.64,0:16:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然和對她的印象不大一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.29,0:16:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 為什麼我要和你一起看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡桃在看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要說悄悄話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦 我也有很多原因的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.72,0:16:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 胡桃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和爽子聊天就會覺得放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心就把內心的話給說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像給人的印象真的改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.81,0:16:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎變的更坦率了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在向我招手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊 是向胡桃招手的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.35,0:17:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生質量還不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.04,0:17:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 貞子旁邊的女孩是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.14,0:17:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡桃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.34,0:17:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 說到貞子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.15,0:17:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的足球比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細看的話 意外的...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.13,0:17:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超可怕 超強力 超級殘影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.26,0:17:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人刮目相看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.62,0:17:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞子強大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.21,0:17:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在表揚她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.79,0:17:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 不叫貞子吧 她的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 不是叫貞子麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼貞子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 前段時間千鶴硬是讓我記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.94,0:17:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是叫...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我離「貴子」遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:17:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該有個記住的辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:18:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想像 漆黑的水邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沼澤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初是Sa行 開頭是Sa
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.95,0:18:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 剛開始是sa
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.49,0:18:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後好像是炊帚的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清爽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.25,0:18:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫爽子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫暗沼爽子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 泥澤嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 是叫黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.16,0:18:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽前先熱身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔太 和我一起熱身沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.33,0:18:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.21,0:18:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天在詞典上查了下「特別」這個詞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.37,0:18:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 詞典
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:18:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「無法像對待其他人那樣」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.59,0:19:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詞典上這麼寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詞典真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.19,0:19:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像聽到了我們的對話一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.65,0:19:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想說什啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 該怎麼說呢 真是複雜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.14,0:19:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為風早同學對我來說就是這樣的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.85,0:19:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實一直被風早同學幫助是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從始至終得到風早同學幫助也是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是無法和其他人相提並論的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是因為你沒和其他的男生接觸才無法進行比較的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.92,0:19:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和其他的男生多聊聊怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生不是有的是嘛 比如座位比較近的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風早同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了是其他的男生了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.84,0:19:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.48,0:19:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像坐在後面或者前面的 總有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.24,0:19:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.74,0:20:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真田同學的話 之前聊過幾句
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.11,0:20:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真田
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.13,0:20:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了哦 接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔球 超special
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍 接的漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁止魔球
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.51,0:20:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我好好投
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.62,0:20:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的對不起 真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.68,0:20:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被救了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.70,0:20:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛嚇呆了 忘記說了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.53,0:20:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好說出來比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.89,0:20:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再和真田多聊聊怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.18,0:21:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 兩人單獨好好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.03,0:21:26.02,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その空一杯の紙飛行機　暗いになって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.03,0:21:26.02,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空中飛滿了紙飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:36.34,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いかない　それが答えてなんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:36.34,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走 那就是回答
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.59,0:21:39.75,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,シャボン玉　飛ばそう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.59,0:21:39.75,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肥皂泡泡 飄飄浮浮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:48.03,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空まではきっと届かない　うちに壊れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:48.03,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還未到達天空就破滅消散而去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.39,0:21:53.56,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いま誰知りたいの永遠じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.39,0:21:53.56,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是我們想要的永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.82,0:22:01.22,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,このままずっと　いていたいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.82,0:22:01.22,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管想要永遠留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.58,0:22:12.49,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その空一杯の紙飛行機　暗いになって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.58,0:22:12.49,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空中飛滿了紙飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.30,0:22:22.03,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ひとつだけ見つけて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.30,0:22:22.03,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只找尋到了屬於我的唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.78,0:22:34.67,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(626,363)}第12話 戀愛感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.02,0:22:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是會在意他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.95,0:22:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.21,0:22:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不斷的追逐他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.34,0:22:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 戀愛感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.10,0:22:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓大家久等的「好想告訴你」DVD第一卷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.64,0:22:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於要在12月23日發售了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.54,0:22:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為初回特典
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.86,0:22:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收錄了Q版爽子 原創插圖卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.92,0:22:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「好想告訴你」秘密交換筆記
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.36,0:22:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還收錄了作為聲音特典的「好想告訴你」spin-off drama
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.79,0:22:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.93,0:23:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你收齊了「好想告訴你」全集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.05,0:23:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能得到椎名輕穗大師的原畫的全集收錄盒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.27,0:23:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為相愛的男女朋友的聖誕禮物之一 請務必算上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.16,0:23:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣愛情就會變的更深
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.11,0:23:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就下周再見
